- **Functionality**: The user types text into an input field. As they type, the reversed string appears below it in real-time. Each character in the reversed string animates in sequentially (e.g., fading in with a slight delay for each character).
- **Layout and Styling**: The design is clean, modern, and centered. It uses a sans-serif font, subtle shadows, borders, and smooth transitions for a polished look. The layout is responsive and works on both desktop and mobile devices.
